- Skin friendly

- Strong hold without skin irritation (Latex-free)

- The unique U-shaped incision design facilitates the fixation of indwelling needle in butterfly wing
- Ultra-thin design for perfect fitting on the skin
- Special ear shope makes paper frame stripping easier.
- Additional record ond breathable tape for fixotion make it easy for operator to record patient name, time and bed No.. and can be used to strengthen the fixation for quality management.
